OL,3,CWeather warnings lifted as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ceases on Easter Sunday
OL,6,FStorm Dave caused road closures and
OL,7,Ftrain disruptions early on Easter
OL,8,FSunday morning, with the forecast
OL,9,Fcalling for clearing throughout the
OL,10,Fday.
OL,12,FAn amber wind warning covering parts
OL,13,Fof northern England, north-west Wales
OL,14,Fand southern Scotland was lifted at
OL,15,F3am, while three yellow warnings
OL,16,Facross parts of northern England,
OL,17,FScotland and Wales were lifted later
OL,18,Fin the morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
