PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775376277
OL,3,CWeather warnings lifted as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ceases on Easter Sunday
OL,6,FThe Met Office's forecast for Easter
OL,7,FSunday said: "Storm Dave will clear
OL,8,Fnortheast on Sunday morning, leaving
OL,9,Fsunshine and widespread showers across
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,F"Northern areas will see the heaviest,
OL,13,Fblustery showers and feel cold, while
OL,14,Ftemperatures elsewhere stay closer to
OL,15,Faverage for early April."
OL,17,FBefore the severe amber weather
OL,18,Fwarning was lifted, the Met Office had
OL,19,Fforecast "severe gales" across central
OL,20,Fand northern areas of the country
OL,21,Fovernight into Sunday.
