PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775376277
OL,3,CWeather warnings lifted as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ceases on Easter Sunday
OL,6,FIn the early hours of Sunday, Traffic
OL,7,FScotland warned that several major
OL,8,Fbridges had restrictions in place due
OL,9,Fto strong winds, including the
OL,10,FQueensferry Crossing on the M90, which
OL,11,Fconnects Edinburgh with Fife and the
OL,12,Fnearby Forth Road Bridge on the A9000.
OL,14,FThe Humber Bridge linking East
OL,15,FYorkshire with north Lincolnshire
OL,16,Freopened after being closed in both
OL,17,Fdirections to high-sided and
OL,18,Fvulnerable vehicles early on Sunday
OL,19,Fdue to strong winds, National Highways
OL,20,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
