FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775376277
OL,3,CWeather warnings lifted as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ceases on Easter Sunday
OL,6,FElsewhere, ScotRail confirmed
OL,7,Femergency speed restrictions would be
OL,8,Fimplemented across parts of its
OL,9,Fnetwork, resulting in longer travel
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,12,FIn England's north, Network Rail
OL,13,FManchester announced rail replacement
OL,14,Fbus services would run between
OL,15,FManchester Picadilly and Chester due
OL,16,Fto overnight weather conditions.
OL,18,FAs of 7am on Sunday, there were four
OL,19,Fcoastal flood warnings and 32 flood
OL,20,Falerts across England and eight
OL,21,Fcoastal flood alerts in Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
