FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775376277
OL,3,CWeather warnings lifted as Storm Dave
OL,4,Ceases on Easter Sunday
OL,6,FIn Scotland, 12 flood warnings and
OL,7,Feight flood alerts remained in place.
OL,9,FThe Energy Networks Association (ENA)
OL,10,F- which represents electricity network
OL,11,Foperators - warned of potential power
OL,12,Fcuts and issued safety advice
OL,13,Ffollowing the weather warnings.
OL,15,FIt said in a statement on Saturday:
OL,16,F"The storm has the potential to affect
OL,17,Flocal power infrastructure, increasing
OL,18,Fthe risk of a power cut and fallen
OL,19,Fpower lines.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
